stimulus:
Welcome to the study!

Click the button below to continue to the 'Experiment Consent Form':

Instructions

.

At the start of every trial, a '+' sign will appear at the centre of the screen, telling you to focus on the centre.

.

.

+

.

.

Click 'Next' to continue to the next instructions:

After, a picture will appear of a scene for a couple of seconds. One of the people's faces will be covered by a white circle like this:

Think about what is happening in the scene and what facial expression is behind the white circle.

.

Click 'Next' to continue to the next instructions:

The screen will automatically change to the response screen.

.

You will have the option of choosing between these 3 different emojis:

Press the key [f, g, h] that corresponds to the emoji you think BEST represents the covered face from the last scene.

.

Click 'Next' to continue to the next instructions:

You will do this for multiple trials.

Try to respond as soon as you know the answer.

.

Once all trials are completed, you will be asked to fill out a quick survey.

All responses will be completely anonymous.

.

Click 'Start' to start the experiment!:

Congratulations! You have completed the first part of the experiment!

This last part is a survey on how you work in the classroom and at home.

Steps:

1) Read the statement.

2) If you think that the statement describes you, click 'Agree'

If you think that the statement DOES NOT describe you, click 'Disagree'.

3) Click the 'Next' button to move on to the next set of questions

4) At the end of the survey, click the 'Submit Survey' button when you have completed all the questions

Thank you for participating in this study!

Click the 'Exit' button below to finish the experiment:
